    "description": "FreakOut Holdings, inc., through its subsidiaries, offers advertising solutions in Japan and internationally. It operates through Advertising Business, Investment Business, Influencer marketing business, and Other Businesses segments. The company develops and sells DSPs and DMPs; data mining, development, and sale of ad applications; and advertisement consultation business. It is also involved in IoT-based digital signage business; global app marketing and public relations; provision of trading desk and monetization platform for digital media; and development and operation of retail in-store media, as well as digital creative and performance agencies businesses. In addition, it operates a data-driven digital agency that specializes in software development, data science, and robot automation. FreakOut Holdings, inc. was formerly known as FreakOut, inc and changed its name to FreakOut Holdings, inc. in January 2017. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Tokyo, Japan."
